I"0<h1 id="实例-1">实例 1</h1>

<p>保留圆周率小数点前 4 位 </p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>
<span class="o">[</span>root@VM_15_187_centos ~]# <span class="nb">echo</span> <span class="s2">"scale=10; a(1)*4"</span> | bc <span class="nt">-l</span> | <span class="nb">awk</span> <span class="s1">'{printf ("%.4f\n", $1)}'</span>
3.1416

</code></pre></div></div>

